  "1702140": {
    "name": "Left to Survive: Zombie Shooter",
    "steam_appid": 1702140,
    "required_age": "18+",
    "is_free": true,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1702140/extras/e8bcb2b4c7124efa43253f8bdd85b08f.avif?t=1770623672\" width=600 height=235 /></span>拿起你的枪，带着你的勇气在终极动作射击游戏《Left to Survive》中生存下来。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >没有什么地方是安全的。</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >使用步枪、手榴弹、霰弹枪和你军火库中的任何东西对抗僵尸以生存下来，确保避难所的安全并拯救幸存者。建立你的营地，以防御敌人的攻击。用直升机摧毁敌人的基地，偷取他们的资源。在单人和团队多人比赛中与其他玩家战斗。跟其他人类派系联合起来。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1702140/extras/57b4694ac83e751fdcc5e76103e0d41b.poster.avif?t=1770623672\" width=625 height=352 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1702140/extras/57b4694ac83e751fdcc5e76103e0d41b.webm?t=1770623672\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >杀死僵尸群</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >使用具有强大火力的武器包拯救被困的幸存者和清除僵尸出没的地区。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1702140/extras/fd52f2c510fa613458b0a5d9bc375c6d.poster.avif?t=1770623672\" width=625 height=352 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1702140/extras/fd52f2c510fa613458b0a5d9bc375c6d.webm?t=1770623672\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >使用直升机摧毁基地。</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >使用直升机在敌人的基地释放一颗炽热的子弹风暴来偷取他们的资源。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >激烈的玩家对战</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >你认为僵尸是危险的吗? 在单人和二对二比赛中测试你的生存技能。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1702140/extras/14858ab8b198a2a2f6e4520ab609bd5a.poster.avif?t=1770623672\" width=625 height=352 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1702140/extras/14858ab8b198a2a2f6e4520ab609bd5a.webm?t=1770623672\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >挑战僵尸魔王。</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >保护自己免受僵尸跳跃的伤害。他们会穿着警察护甲或有毒气体爆炸。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1702140/extras/ccee3ac0db4b4ae6be3e5129aea4ca6d.poster.avif?t=1770623672\" width=625 height=352 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1702140/extras/ccee3ac0db4b4ae6be3e5129aea4ca6d.webm?t=1770623672\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >建立和定制你的基地。</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >建立，定制，并保护你的营地使其不被僵尸和敌对派系所伤害。找到幸存者，掠夺材料并联合起一起克服后末日世界。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >游戏包含随机物品。</p>",
